01.10 S C=0
01.20 T %4
01.30 F N=3,2,996;D 2
01.40 T "AMOUNT OF COUSIN PRIME PAIRS",C,!
01.50 Q

02.10 S P=N;D 3;S D=A
02.20 S P=N+4;D 3
02.30 I (-A*D)2.4;R
02.40 T N,P,!
02.50 S C=C+1

03.10 S K=2
03.20 I (K-P)3.3;S A=-1;R
03.30 S B=P/K
03.40 I (FITR(B)-B)3.5,3.7,3.5
03.50 S K=K+1
03.60 G 3.2
03.70 S A=0
